Bead is missing required FFT fields:
  - Profile (must be BUILD|INVESTIGATE|REPAIR|EVOLVE)
  - Security sensitive (must be true|false)
  - Complexity source (must be essential|accidental)
  - Decision trace (must contain path to trace file)
  - Deterministic checks (list of checks routed to scripts)
  - Turbulence (loop cycle counts)

All beads must include FFT decision backbone fields.
See references/fft-decision-trees.md for the full FFT specification.
